HEADWORD: Invertin
<hw>In*vert"in</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Physiol.
Chem.)</fld> <def>An enzyme which causes cane sugar to take up a
molecule of water and be converted into invert sugar.</def>⟦br⟧
